A. Linear-probe evaluation
A. 线性探针评估

We provide additional details for linear probe experiments presented in this paper, including the list of the datasets and models used for evaluation.
我们为本文中提出的线性探针实验提供了更多细节，包括用于评估的数据集和模型列表。

A.1. Datasets  A.1. 数据集

We use the 12 datasets from the well-studied evaluation suite introduced by (Kornblith et al., 2019) and add 15 additional datasets in order to assess the performance of models on a wider variety of distributions and tasks. These datasets include MNIST, the Facial Expression Recognition 2013 dataset (Goodfellow et al., 2015), STL-10 (Coates et al., 2011), EuroSAT (Helber et al., 2019), the NWPURESISC45 dataset (Cheng et al., 2017), the German Traffic Sign Recognition Benchmark (GTSRB) dataset (Stallkamp et al., 2011), the KITTI dataset (Geiger et al., 2012), PatchCamelyon (Veeling et al., 2018), the UCF101 action recognition dataset (Soomro et al., 2012), Kinetics 700 (Carreira et al., 2019), 2,500 random samples of the CLEVR dataset (Johnson et al., 2017), the Hateful Memes dataset (Kiela et al., 2020), and the ImageNet-1k dataset (Deng et al., 2012). For the two video datasets (UCF101 and Kinetics700), we use the middle frame of each video clip as the input image. STL-10 and UCF101 have multiple predefined train/validation/test splits, 10 and 3 respectively, and we report the average over all splits. Details on each dataset and the corresponding evaluation metrics are provided in Table 9.
我们采用了(Kornblith 等人，2019)提出的经过充分研究的评估套件中的 12 个数据集，并新增了 15 个数据集，以评估模型在更广泛分布和任务上的性能。这些数据集包括 MNIST、面部表情识别 2013 数据集(Goodfellow 等人，2015)、STL-10(Coates 等人，2011)、EuroSAT(Helber 等人，2019)、NWPURESISC45 数据集(Cheng 等人，2017)、德国交通标志识别基准(GTSRB)数据集(Stallkamp 等人，2011)、KITTI 数据集(Geiger 等人，2012)、PatchCamelyon(Veeling 等人，2018)、UCF101 动作识别数据集(Soomro 等人，2012)、Kinetics 700(Carreira 等人，2019)、CLEVR 数据集(Johnson 等人，2017)的 2500 个随机样本、Hateful Memes 数据集(Kiela 等人，2020)以及 ImageNet-1k 数据集(Deng 等人，2012)。对于两个视频数据集(UCF101 和 Kinetics700)，我们使用每个视频片段的中间帧作为输入图像。STL-10 和 UCF101 分别有 10 个和 3 个预定义的训练/验证/测试划分，我们报告所有划分的平均结果。 各数据集的详细信息及相应评估指标见表 9。
Additionally, we created two datasets that we call Country211 and Rendered SST2. The Country211 dataset is designed to assess the geolocation capability of visual representations. We filtered the YFCC100m dataset (Thomee et al., 2016) to find 211 countries (defined as having an ISO-3166 country code) that have at least 300 photos with GPS coordinates, and we built a balanced dataset with 211 categories, by sampling 200 photos for training and 100 photos for testing, for each country.
此外，我们创建了两个数据集，分别命名为 Country211 和 Rendered SST2。Country211 数据集旨在评估视觉表征的地理定位能力。我们对 YFCC100m 数据集（Thomee 等人，2016 年）进行筛选，找出拥有至少 300 张带 GPS 坐标照片的 211 个国家（以拥有 ISO-3166 国家代码为准），并通过为每个国家采样 200 张训练照片和 100 张测试照片，构建了一个包含 211 个类别的平衡数据集。
The Rendered SST2 dataset is designed to measure the optical character recognition capability of visual representations. To do so, we used the sentences from the Stanford Sentiment Treebank dataset (Socher et al., 2013) and rendered them into images, with black texts on a white background, in a 448 × 448 448 × 448 448 xx448448 \times 448 resolution. Two example images from this dataset are shown in Figure 19.
Rendered SST2 数据集旨在衡量视觉表征的光学字符识别能力。为此，我们使用斯坦福情感树库数据集（Socher 等人，2013 年）中的句子，将其渲染成图像——白色背景上显示黑色文字，分辨率为 448 × 448 448 × 448 448 xx448448 \times 448 。图 19 展示了该数据集的两个示例图像。

A.2. Models  A.2. 模型

In combination with the datasets listed above, we evaluate the following series of models using linear probes.
结合上述列出的数据集，我们使用线性探针评估以下系列模型。
LM RN50 This is a multimodal model that uses an autoregressive loss instead of a contrastive loss, while using
LM RN50 这是一种多模态模型，采用自回归损失而非对比损失，同时沿用最小对比模型中的 ResNet-50 架构。
the ResNet-50 architecture as in the smallest contrastive model. To do so, the output from the CNN is projected into four tokens, which are then fed as a prefix to a language model autoregressively predicting the text tokens. Apart from the training objective, the model was trained on the same dataset for the same number of epochs as other CLIP models.
具体实现中，CNN 的输出被投影为四个标记，随后作为前缀输入至语言模型，自回归地预测文本标记。除训练目标外，该模型与其他 CLIP 模型在相同数据集上训练了相同周期数。
CLIP-RN Five ResNet-based contrastive CLIP models are included. As discussed in the paper, the first two models follow ResNet-50 and ResNet-101, and we use EfficientNetstyle (Tan & Le, 2019) scaling for the next three models which simultaneously scale the model width, the number of layers, and the input resolution to obtain models with roughly 4 x , 16 x 4 x , 16 x 4x,16 x4 x, 16 x, and 64 x 64 x 64 x64 x computation.
CLIP-RN 包含五个基于 ResNet 的对比 CLIP 模型。如论文所述，前两个模型遵循 ResNet-50 和 ResNet-101 架构，后三个模型采用 EfficientNet 风格（Tan & Le, 2019）的缩放策略，同步调整模型宽度、层数和输入分辨率，以获得计算量分别约为 4 x , 16 x 4 x , 16 x 4x,16 x4 x, 16 x 和 64 x 64 x 64 x64 x 的模型。
CLIP-ViT We include four CLIP models that use the Vision Transformer (Dosovitskiy et al., 2020) architecture as the image encoder. We include three models trained on 224-by-224 pixel images: ViT-B/32, ViT-B/16, ViT-L/14, and the ViT-L/14 model fine-tuned on 336-by-336 pixel input images.
CLIP-ViT 我们包含了四个采用 Vision Transformer（Dosovitskiy 等人，2020）架构作为图像编码器的 CLIP 模型。其中包括三个基于 224×224 像素图像训练的模型：ViT-B/32、ViT-B/16、ViT-L/14，以及一个在 336×336 像素输入图像上微调的 ViT-L/14 模型。
EfficietNet We use the nine models (B0-B8) from the original EfficientNet paper (Tan & Le, 2019), as well as the noisy-student variants (B0-B7, L2-475, and L2-800) (Tan & Le, 2019). The largest models (L2-475 and L2-800) take the input resolutions of 475 × 475 475 × 475 475 xx475475 \times 475 and 800 × 800 800 × 800 800 xx800800 \times 800 pixels, respectively.
EfficientNet 我们使用了原始 EfficientNet 论文（Tan & Le，2019）中的九个模型（B0-B8），以及其噪声学生变体（B0-B7、L2-475 和 L2-800）（Tan & Le，2019）。最大模型（L2-475 和 L2-800）分别接受 475 × 475 475 × 475 475 xx475475 \times 475 和 800 × 800 800 × 800 800 xx800800 \times 800 像素的输入分辨率。
Instagram-pretrained ResNeXt We use the four models ( 32 x 8 d , 32 x 16 d , 32 x 32 d , 32 x 48 d 32 x 8 d , 32 x 16 d , 32 x 32 d , 32 x 48 d 32x8d,32x16d,32x32d,32x48d32 \mathrm{x} 8 \mathrm{~d}, 32 \mathrm{x} 16 \mathrm{~d}, 32 \mathrm{x} 32 \mathrm{~d}, 32 \mathrm{x} 48 \mathrm{~d} ) released by (Mahajan et al., 2018), as well as their two FixRes variants which use higher input resolutions (Touvron et al., 2019).
Instagram 预训练 ResNeXt 我们使用了（Mahajan 等人，2018）发布的四个模型（ 32 x 8 d , 32 x 16 d , 32 x 32 d , 32 x 48 d 32 x 8 d , 32 x 16 d , 32 x 32 d , 32 x 48 d 32x8d,32x16d,32x32d,32x48d32 \mathrm{x} 8 \mathrm{~d}, 32 \mathrm{x} 16 \mathrm{~d}, 32 \mathrm{x} 32 \mathrm{~d}, 32 \mathrm{x} 48 \mathrm{~d} ），以及它们两个采用更高输入分辨率的 FixRes 变体（Touvron 等人，2019）。
Big Transfer (BiT) We use BiT-S and BiT-M models (Kolesnikov et al., 2019), trained on the ImageNet-1k and ImageNet-21k datasets. The model weights for BiT-L is not publicly available.
大迁移（BiT） 我们使用了在 ImageNet-1k 和 ImageNet-21k 数据集上训练的 BiT-S 和 BiT-M 模型（Kolesnikov 等人，2019）。BiT-L 的模型权重未公开提供。
Vision Transformer (ViT) We also include four ViT (Dosovitskiy et al., 2020) checkpoints pretrained on the ImageNet-21k dataset, namely ViT-B/32, ViT-B/16, ViT L / 16 L / 16 L//16\mathrm{L} / 16, and ViT-H/14. We note that their best-performing models, trained on the JFT-300M dataset, are not available publicly.
视觉 Transformer（ViT）我们还包含了四个在 ImageNet-21k 数据集上预训练的 ViT（Dosovitskiy 等人，2020）检查点，分别是 ViT-B/32、ViT-B/16、ViT L / 16 L / 16 L//16\mathrm{L} / 16 和 ViT-H/14。需要注意的是，它们在 JFT-300M 数据集上训练的最佳性能模型并未公开提供。
SimCLRv2 The SimCLRv2 (Chen et al., 2020c) project released pre-trained and fine-tuned models in various settings. We use the seven pretrain-only checkpoints with selective kernels.
SimCLRv2 项目（Chen 等人，2020c）发布了多种设置下的预训练及微调模型。我们采用了七个仅预训练且带有选择性核的检查点。
BYOL We use the recently released model weights of BYOL (Grill et al., 2020), specifically their 50x1 and 200x2
我们使用了 BYOL（Grill 等人，2020）最新发布的模型权重，具体是其 50x1 和 200x2 版本。
Figure 19. Two example images from the Rendered SST2 dataset
图 19. 来自 Rendered SST2 数据集的两张示例图像
checkpoints.  检查点。
Momentum Contrast (MoCo) We include the MoCo-v1 (He et al., 2020) and the MoCo-v2 (Chen et al., 2020d) checkpoints.
动量对比（MoCo）我们包含了 MoCo-v1（He 等人，2020 年）和 MoCo-v2（Chen 等人，2020d）的检查点。
VirTex We use the pretrained model of VirTex (Desai & Johnson, 2020). We note that VirTex has a similar model design to CLIP-AR but is trained on a 1000x smaller dataset of high-quality captions from MSCOCO.
VirTex 我们使用了 VirTex（Desai & Johnson，2020 年）的预训练模型。我们注意到 VirTex 的模型设计与 CLIP-AR 类似，但训练数据集规模小 1000 倍，使用的是来自 MSCOCO 的高质量标注数据。
ResNet We add the original ResNet checkpoints released by (He et al., 2016b), namely ResNet-50, ResNet-101, and ResNet152.
ResNet 我们添加了由（He 等人，2016b）发布的原始 ResNet 检查点，即 ResNet-50、ResNet-101 和 ResNet152。

A.3. Evaluation  A.3. 评估

We use image features taken from the penultimate layer of each model, ignoring any classification layer provided. For CLIP-ViT models, we used the features before the linear projection to the embedding space, which corresponds to I_f in Figure 3. We train a logistic regression classifier using scikit-learn’s L-BFGS implementation, with maximum 1,000 iterations, and report the corresponding metric for each dataset. We determine the L 2 regularization strength λ λ lambda\lambda using a hyperparameter sweep on the validation sets over the range between 10 − 6 10 − 6 10^(-6)10^{-6} and 10 6 10 6 10^(6)10^{6}, with 96 logarithmically spaced steps. To save compute required for the sweeps, we perform a parametric binary search that starts with λ = [ 10 − 6 , 10 − 4 , 10 − 2 , 1 , 10 2 , 10 4 , 10 6 ] λ = 10 − 6 , 10 − 4 , 10 − 2 , 1 , 10 2 , 10 4 , 10 6 lambda=[10^(-6),10^(-4),10^(-2),1,10^(2),10^(4),10^(6)]\lambda=\left[10^{-6}, 10^{-4}, 10^{-2}, 1,10^{2}, 10^{4}, 10^{6}\right] and iteratively halves the interval around the peak until it reaches a resolution of 8 steps per decade. The hyperparameter sweeps are performed on a validation split of each dataset. For the datasets that contain a validation split in addition to
我们采用各模型倒数第二层提取的图像特征，忽略其提供的任何分类层。对于 CLIP-ViT 模型，我们使用线性投影至嵌入空间前的特征（对应图 3 中的 I_f）。通过 scikit-learn 的 L-BFGS 实现训练逻辑回归分类器，最大迭代次数设为 1,000 次，并报告各数据集对应指标。L2 正则化强度 λ λ lambda\lambda 通过在验证集上进行超参数扫描确定，范围介于 10 − 6 10 − 6 10^(-6)10^{-6} 至 10 6 10 6 10^(6)10^{6} 之间，按对数尺度分 96 步。为节省扫描计算量，采用参数化二分搜索法：初始值为 λ = [ 10 − 6 , 10 − 4 , 10 − 2 , 1 , 10 2 , 10 4 , 10 6 ] λ = 10 − 6 , 10 − 4 , 10 − 2 , 1 , 10 2 , 10 4 , 10 6 lambda=[10^(-6),10^(-4),10^(-2),1,10^(2),10^(4),10^(6)]\lambda=\left[10^{-6}, 10^{-4}, 10^{-2}, 1,10^{2}, 10^{4}, 10^{6}\right] ，随后围绕峰值逐次将区间减半，直至达到每十倍频 8 步的分辨率。超参数扫描基于各数据集的验证集划分执行。对于额外包含验证集划分的数据集，
a test split, we use the provided validation set to perform the hyperparameter search, and for the datasets that do not provide a validation split or have not published labels for the test data, we split the training dataset to perform the hyperparameter search. For the final result, we combine the validation split back with the training split and report the performance on the unused split.
在测试划分中，我们使用提供的验证集进行超参数搜索；对于未提供验证划分或未发布测试数据标签的数据集，则通过拆分训练数据集来完成超参数搜索。最终结果阶段，我们将验证集重新合并至训练集，并在未使用的划分上报告性能表现。

A.4. Results  A.4. 结果

The individual linear probe scores are provided in Table 10 and plotted in Figure 20. The best-performing CLIP model, using ViT-L/14 archiecture and 336-by-336 pixel images, achieved the state of the art in 21 of the 27 datasets, i.e. included in the Clopper-Pearson 99.5 % 99.5 % 99.5%99.5 \% confidence interval around each dataset’s top score. For many datasets, CLIP performs significantly better than other models, demonstrating the advantage of natural language supervision over traditional pre-training approaches based on image classification. See Section 3.2 for more discussions on the linear probe results.
线性探测单项得分详见表 10 及图 20。采用 ViT-L/14 架构和 336×336 像素图像的最佳性能 CLIP 模型，在 27 个数据集中的 21 个上达到当前最优水平（即包含在 Clopper-Pearson 99.5 % 99.5 % 99.5%99.5 \% 置信区间内，该区间基于各数据集最高得分计算）。对于多数数据集，CLIP 显著优于其他模型，这证明了自然语言监督相较于传统基于图像分类的预训练方法的优势。线性探测结果更多讨论详见第 3.2 节。

B. Zero-Shot Prediction  B. 零样本预测

To provide a qualitative summary / overview of CLIP’s zeroshot performance we visualize a randomly selected prediction for 36 different zero-shot CLIP classifiers in Figure 21. In addition, Table 11 and Figure 22 show the individual zero-shot performance scores for each dataset.
为了对 CLIP 的零样本性能进行定性总结/概述，我们在图 21 中可视化展示了随机选取的 36 个不同零样本 CLIP 分类器的预测结果。此外，表 11 和图 22 分别展示了各数据集的独立零样本性能评分。

C. Duplicate Detector  C. 重复检测器

Our early attempts at duplicate detection and analysis used nearest neighbors in the model’s learned embedding space. While it is intuitive to use a model’s own notion of similarity, we encountered issues. We found the model’s feature space is weighted very heavily towards semantic similarity. Many false positives occurred due to distinct objects that would be described similarly (soccer balls, flowers of the same species, etc…) having almost perfect similarity. We also observed the model was quite poor at assigning certain kinds of near-duplicates high similarity scores. We noticed repeatedly that images with high-frequency textures (such as fur or stripe patterns) pre-processed by different resizing algorithms (nearest neighbor vs bi-linear) could have surprisingly low similarity. This resulted in many false negatives.
我们早期尝试的重复检测和分析方法采用了模型学习到的嵌入空间中的最近邻搜索。虽然利用模型自身的相似性概念很直观，但我们遇到了问题。发现模型的特征空间严重偏向语义相似性，导致许多误判——例如语义描述相似但实际不同的物体（足球、同种花卉等）会获得近乎完美的相似度评分。同时，模型在给某些近似重复项分配高相似度分数时表现欠佳。我们多次观察到，经过不同重采样算法（最近邻 vs 双线性）预处理的高频纹理图像（如毛发或条纹图案），其相似度得分可能意外偏低，从而产生大量漏检。
We built our own near-duplicate detector to fix this issue. We created a synthetic data augmentation pipeline that combined a variety of common image manipulations. The augmentation pipeline combines random cropping and zooming, aspect ratio distortion, downsizing and upscaling to different resolutions, minor rotations, jpeg compression, and HSV color jitter. The pipeline also randomly selects from different interpolation algorithms for all relevant steps. We then trained a model to maximize the similarity of an image and its transformed variant while minimizing similarity to all other images in a training batch. We used the same n-pair / InfoNCE loss as CLIP but with a fixed temperature of 0.07.
我们构建了自己的近重复检测器来解决这个问题。我们创建了一个合成数据增强流程，该流程结合了多种常见的图像处理操作。增强流程包括随机裁剪和缩放、宽高比扭曲、降采样和上采样至不同分辨率、轻微旋转、JPEG 压缩以及 HSV 色彩抖动。该流程还会在所有相关步骤中随机选择不同的插值算法。随后，我们训练了一个模型，旨在最大化图像与其变换版本之间的相似度，同时最小化与训练批次中所有其他图像的相似度。我们采用了与 CLIP 相同的 n-pair/InfoNCE 损失函数，但温度参数固定为 0.07。
We selected a ResNet-50 as the model architecture. We modified the base ResNet-50 with the anti-alias improvements from (Zhang, 2019) and used weight norm (Salimans & Kingma, 2016) instead of batch norm (Ioffe & Szegedy, 2015) to avoid leaking information about duplicates via batch statistics - a problem previously noted in (Henaff, 2020). We also found the GELU activation function (Hendrycks & Gimpel, 2016) to perform better for this task. We trained the model with a total batch size of 1,712 for approximately 30 million images sampled from our pretraining dataset. At the end of training it achieves nearly 100 % 100 % 100%100 \% accuracy on its proxy training task.
我们选择了 ResNet-50 作为模型架构。基于 Zhang(2019)提出的抗锯齿改进方案对基础 ResNet-50 进行了调整，并采用权重归一化(Salimans & Kingma, 2016)替代批归一化(Ioffe & Szegedy, 2015)，以避免通过批次统计量泄露重复样本信息——这个问题在 Henaff(2020)中已被指出。我们还发现 GELU 激活函数(Hendrycks & Gimpel, 2016)在该任务中表现更优。模型训练时使用总批次大小为 1,712，从预训练数据集中采样约 3000 万张图像。训练结束时，其代理训练任务的准确率接近 100 % 100 % 100%100 \% 。

Table 12. CLIP performs similarly when trained on only YFCC100M. Comparing a ResNet-50 trained on only YFCC100M with a same sized subset of WIT shows similar average performance and number of wins on zero shot and linear classifier evals. However, large differences in dataset specific performance occur. We include performance on the 3 datasets where YFCC does best and worst compared to WIT according to a linear probe in order to highlight this as well as aggregate performance across all linear and zero-shot evals and the canonical ImageNet dataset.
表 12. CLIP 在仅使用 YFCC100M 训练时表现相似。将仅在 YFCC100M 上训练的 ResNet-50 与 WIT 相同规模子集对比，在零样本和线性分类器评估中显示出相近的平均性能和胜场数。然而，在特定数据集上的性能存在显著差异。我们根据线性探针评估，纳入了 YFCC 表现最佳和最差的 3 个数据集性能，以突出这一点，同时汇总了所有线性及零样本评估以及经典 ImageNet 数据集的整体表现。

D. Dataset Ablation on YFCC100M
D. 在 YFCC100M 数据集上的消融实验

To study whether our custom dataset is critical to the performance of CLIP, we trained a model on a filtered subset of the YFCC100M dataset (details described in Section 2.2) and compared its performance to the same model trained on an equally sized subset of WIT. We train each model for 32 epochs at which point transfer performance begins to plateau due to overfitting. Results are shown in Table 12. Across our whole eval suite, YFCC and WIT perform similarly on average for both zero-shot and linear probe settings. However, performance on specific fine-grained classification datasets can vary widely - sometimes by over 10 % 10 % 10%10 \%. Our speculation is that these differences in performance reflect the relative density of relevant data in each pre-training dataset. For instance, pre-training on YFCC100M, which might contain many photos of birds and flowers (common subjects for photographers), results in better performance on Birdsnap and Flowers102, while pre-training on WIT results in better car and pet classifiers (which appear common in our dataset).
为验证自定义数据集对 CLIP 模型性能的关键作用，我们在 YFCC100M 的过滤子集（详见 2.2 节）上训练模型，并与同等规模的 WIT 子集训练结果进行对比。每个模型训练 32 个周期，此时迁移性能因过拟合开始趋于稳定。结果如表 12 所示：整体评估中，YFCC 与 WIT 在零样本学习和线性探测设置下表现相近，但在细粒度分类任务上差异显著——某些数据集性能差距甚至超过 10 % 10 % 10%10 \% 。我们推测这种差异源于预训练数据集中相关数据的分布密度差异。例如，YFCC100M 可能包含大量鸟类和花卉照片（摄影常见主题），因此在 Birdsnap 和 Flowers102 上表现更优；而 WIT 预训练则提升了汽车和宠物分类器的性能（这些主题在我们的数据集中更为常见）。
Overall, these results are encouraging as they suggest our approach can use any reasonably filtered collection of paired (text, image) data. This mirrors recent work which reported positive results using the same contrastive pre-training objective on the relatively different domain of medical imaging (Zhang et al., 2020). It also is similar to the findings of noisy student self-training which reported only slight improvements when using their JFT300M dataset over YFCC100M (Xie et al., 2020). We suspect the major advantage of our dataset over the already existing YFCC100M is its much larger size.
总体而言，这些结果令人鼓舞，因为它们表明我们的方法可以利用任何经过合理过滤的（文本、图像）配对数据集合。这与近期在医学影像这一相对不同领域使用相同对比预训练目标获得积极成果的研究相呼应（Zhang 等人，2020）。该发现也与噪声学生自训练的结论类似——后者报告使用 JFT300M 数据集相较于 YFCC100M 仅带来轻微提升（Xie 等人，2020）。我们推测本数据集相较于现有 YFCC100M 的主要优势在于其更大的规模。
Finally, we caution that WIT includes this filtered subset of YFCC100M. This could result in our ablation underestimating the size of performance differences between YFCC100M and the rest of WIT. We do not think this is likely as YFCC100M is only 3.7 % 3.7 % 3.7%3.7 \% of the overall WIT data blend and it did not noticeably change the performance of models when it was added to the existing data blend during the creation of WIT.
最后需要说明的是，WIT 包含了 YFCC100M 的这个过滤子集。这可能导致我们的消融实验低估了 YFCC100M 与 WIT 其余部分之间的性能差异。我们认为这种情况不太可能发生，因为 YFCC100M 仅占 WIT 整体数据混合的 3.7 % 3.7 % 3.7%3.7 \% ，且在 WIT 创建过程中将其添加到现有数据混合时，并未显著改变模型性能。

E. Selected Task and Dataset Results
E. 选定任务及数据集结果

Due to the large variety of datasets and experiments considered in this work, the main body focuses on summarizing and analyzing overall results. In the following subsections we report details of performance for specific groups of tasks, datasets, and evaluation settings.
鉴于本研究所涉及的数据集和实验种类繁多，正文部分主要集中于对整体结果的总结与分析。后续小节将详细报告特定任务组、数据集及评估设置下的性能细节。

E.1. Image and Text Retrieval
E.1. 图像与文本检索

CLIP pre-trains for the task of image-text retrieval on our noisy web-scale dataset. Although the focus of this paper is on representation learning and task learning for the purpose of transfer to a wide variety of downstream datasets, validating that CLIP is able to achieve high transfer performance transfer on exactly what it is pre-trained for is an important sanity check / proof of concept. In Table 13 we check the zero-shot transfer performance of CLIP for both text and image retrieval on the Flickr30k and MSCOCO datsets. Zero-shot CLIP matches or outperforms all prior zero-shot results on these two datasets. Zero-shot CLIP is also competitive with the current overall SOTA for the task of text retrieval on Flickr30k. On image retrieval, CLIP’s performance relative to the overall state of the art is noticeably lower. However, zero-shot CLIP is still competitive with a fine-tuned Unicoder-VL. On the larger MS-COCO dataset fine-tuning improves performance significantly and zero-shot CLIP is not competitive with the most recent work. For both these datasets we prepend the prompt “a photo of” to the description of each image which we found boosts CLIP’s zero-shot R@1 performance between 1 and 2 points.
CLIP 在我们的噪声网络规模数据集上针对图像-文本检索任务进行了预训练。尽管本文的重点在于表征学习和任务学习，目的是为了迁移到各种下游数据集，但验证 CLIP 能否在其预训练目标上实现高迁移性能是一项重要的概念验证/合理性检查。在表 13 中，我们检验了 CLIP 在 Flickr30k 和 MSCOCO 数据集上针对文本和图像检索的零样本迁移性能。零样本 CLIP 在这两个数据集上匹配或超越了所有先前的零样本结果。对于 Flickr30k 上的文本检索任务，零样本 CLIP 也与当前整体最先进技术（SOTA）具有竞争力。在图像检索方面，CLIP 相对于整体最先进技术的表现明显较低。然而，零样本 CLIP 仍能与经过微调的 Unicoder-VL 相媲美。在更大的 MS-COCO 数据集上，微调显著提升了性能，零样本 CLIP 与最新工作相比不具备竞争力。 针对这两个数据集，我们在每张图像的描述前添加了提示语“一张照片”，发现这能将 CLIP 的零样本 R@1 性能提升 1 到 2 个百分点。

E.2. Optical Character Recognition
E.2. 光学字符识别

Although visualizations have shown that ImageNet models contain features that respond to the presence of text in an image (Zeiler & Fergus, 2014), these representations are not sufficiently fine-grained to use for the task of optical character recognition (OCR). To compensate, models are augmented with the outputs of custom OCR engines and features to boost performance on tasks where this capability is required (Singh et al., 2019; Yang et al., 2020). Early during the development of CLIP, we noticed that CLIP began to learn primitive OCR capabilities which appeared to steadily improve over the course of the project. To evaluate this qualitatively noticed behavior, we measured performance
尽管可视化研究表明 ImageNet 模型包含对图像中文字存在响应的特征（Zeiler & Fergus, 2014），但这些表征尚不足以精细到用于光学字符识别（OCR）任务。为此，模型会结合定制 OCR 引擎的输出及额外特征来增强需要此能力的任务表现（Singh 等, 2019；Yang 等, 2020）。在 CLIP 项目早期，我们注意到 CLIP 开始学习初级的 OCR 能力，且该能力随着项目推进持续提升。为定量评估这一观察到的现象，我们测量了其性能表现
on 5 datasets requiring the direct and indirect use of OCR. Three of these datasets MNIST (LeCun), SVHN (Netzer et al., 2011), and IIIT5K (Mishra et al., 2012) directly check the ability of a model to perform low-level character and word recognition, while Hateful Memes (Kiela et al., 2020) and SST-2 (Socher et al., 2013) check the ability of a model to use OCR to perform a semantic task. Results are reported in Table 14.
在 5 个需要直接或间接使用 OCR 的数据集上。其中三个数据集 MNIST（LeCun）、SVHN（Netzer 等人，2011）和 IIIT5K（Mishra 等人，2012）直接测试模型执行低级字符和单词识别的能力，而 Hateful Memes（Kiela 等人，2020）和 SST-2（Socher 等人，2013）则测试模型利用 OCR 执行语义任务的能力。结果如表 14 所示。
CLIP’s performance is still highly variable and appears to be sensitive to some combination of the domain (rendered or natural images) and the type of text to be recognized (numbers or words). CLIP’s OCR performance is strongest Hateful Memes and SST-2 - datasets where the text is digitally rendered and consists mostly of words. On IIIT5K, which is natural images of individually cropped words, zero-shot CLIP performs a bit more respectively and its performance is similar to Jaderberg et al. (2014) early work combining deep learning and structured prediction to perform openvocabulary OCR. However, performance is noticeably lower on two datasets involving recognition of hand written and street view numbers. CLIP’s 51 % 51 % 51%51 \% accuracy on full number SVHN is well below any published results. Inspection suggests CLIP struggles with repeated characters as well as the low resolution and blurry images of SVHN. CLIP’s zeroshot MNIST performance is also poor and is outperformed by supervised logistic regression on raw pixels, one of the simplest possible machine learning baselines.
CLIP 的性能仍然存在较大波动，且似乎对领域（渲染图像或自然图像）与待识别文本类型（数字或单词）的某种组合较为敏感。在 Hateful Memes 和 SST-2 数据集上——这些数据集的文本为数字渲染且主要由单词组成——CLIP 的 OCR 表现最为强劲。而在 IIIT5K（包含单独裁剪单词的自然图像）上，零样本 CLIP 的表现稍逊，其性能与 Jaderberg 等人（2014 年）早期结合深度学习与结构化预测进行开放词汇 OCR 的研究相近。然而，在涉及手写和街景数字识别的两个数据集上，CLIP 的表现明显较差。CLIP 在完整数字 SVHN 上的 51 % 51 % 51%51 \% 准确率远低于任何已发表结果。观察表明，CLIP 在处理重复字符以及 SVHN 低分辨率模糊图像时存在困难。CLIP 的零样本 MNIST 性能同样不佳，甚至被基于原始像素的监督逻辑回归（最简单的机器学习基线之一）超越。
SST-2 is a sentence level NLP dataset which we render into images. We include SST-2 in order to check whether CLIP is able to convert low level OCR capability into a higher level representation. Fitting a linear classifier on CLIP’s representation of rendered sentences achives 80.5 % 80.5 % 80.5%80.5 \% accuracy. This is on par with the 80 % 80 % 80%80 \% accuracy of a continuous bag of words baseline using GloVe word vectors pre-trained on 840 billion tokens (Pennington et al., 2014). While this is a simple NLP baseline by today’s standard, and well below the 97.5 % 97.5 % 97.5%97.5 \% of the current SOTA, it is encouraging to see that CLIP is able to turn an image of rendered text into a non-trivial sentence level representation. Fully supervised CLIP is also surprisingly strong on Hateful Meme detection, where CLIP is only 0.7 points behind the current single model SOTA and several points above the best baseline from the original paper. Similar to SST-2, these other results on Hateful Memes use the ground truth text which CLIP does not have access to. Finally, we note that zero-shot CLIP outperforms the best results using fully supervised linear probes across all other 56 models included in our evaluation suite. This suggests CLIP’s OCR capability is at least somewhat unique compared to existing work on self-supervised and supervised representation learning.
SST-2 是一个句子级 NLP 数据集，我们将其渲染为图像。包含 SST-2 是为了检验 CLIP 能否将低级 OCR 能力转化为高级表征。在 CLIP 渲染句子的表征上拟合线性分类器达到了 80.5 % 80.5 % 80.5%80.5 \% 准确率，这与使用 8400 亿 token 预训练的 GloVe 词向量（Pennington 等人，2014 年）的连续词袋基线 80 % 80 % 80%80 \% 准确率相当。虽然以当今标准来看这是一个简单的 NLP 基线，远低于当前 SOTA 的 97.5 % 97.5 % 97.5%97.5 \% ，但令人鼓舞的是 CLIP 能将渲染文本图像转化为有效的句子级表征。全监督 CLIP 在恶意表情包检测任务上也表现出惊人实力，仅比当前单模型 SOTA 低 0.7 分，且比原论文最佳基线高出数分。与 SST-2 类似，这些恶意表情包的其他结果使用了 CLIP 无法接触的真实文本。最后我们注意到，零样本 CLIP 在我们评估套件包含的其他 56 个模型中，全面超越了全监督线性探针的最佳结果。 这表明 CLIP 的 OCR 能力与现有的自监督和监督表示学习工作相比至少具有一定独特性。

E.3. Action Recognition in Videos
E.3. 视频中的动作识别

For the purpose of learning, a potentially important aspect of natural language is its ability to express, and therefore supervise, an extremely wide set of concepts. A CLIP model, since it is trained to pair semi-arbitrary text with images, is likely to receive supervision for a wide range of visual concepts involving both common and proper nouns, verbs, and adjectives. ImageNet-1K, by contrast, only labels common nouns. Does the lack of broader supervision in ImageNet result in weaker transfer of ImageNet models to tasks involving the recognition of visual concepts that are not nouns?
就学习目的而言，自然语言一个潜在的重要特性是其能够表达并监督极其广泛的概念集合。CLIP 模型由于训练目的是将半任意文本与图像配对，可能会接收到涉及普通名词、专有名词、动词和形容词的广泛视觉概念的监督信号。相比之下，ImageNet-1K 仅标注普通名词。ImageNet 中缺乏更广泛的监督，是否会导致其模型在识别非名词类视觉概念的任务上迁移性能较弱？
To investigate this, we measure and compare the performance of CLIP and ImageNet models on several video
为了研究这一点，我们测量并比较了 CLIP 和 ImageNet 模型在多个视频上的性能

action classification datasets which measure the ability of a model to recognize verbs. In Table 15 we report results on UCF-101 (Soomro et al., 2012) and Kinetics-700 (Carreira et al., 2019), two common datasets for the task. Unfortunately, our CPU based linear classifier takes a prohibitively long time to evaluate on a video dataset due to the very large number of training frames. To deal with this, we aggressively sub-sample each video to only a single center frame, effectively turning it into an image classification dataset. As a result, our reported performance in a linear evaluation setting likely under estimates performance by a moderate amount.
动作分类数据集用于衡量模型识别动词的能力。表 15 中我们报告了在 UCF-101（Soomro 等人，2012）和 Kinetics-700（Carreira 等人，2019）这两个该任务常用数据集上的结果。遗憾的是，由于训练帧数量极其庞大，我们基于 CPU 的线性分类器在视频数据集上的评估耗时过长。为解决此问题，我们对每段视频进行激进的下采样，仅保留中间单帧，实质上将其转化为图像分类数据集。因此，在线性评估设置下报告的性能可能被适度低估。

表 16. ImageNet 鲁棒性性能详表。IN 作为 ImageNet 的缩写使用。 a a ^(a){ }^{a} （Xie 等人，2020） b b ^(b){ }^{b} （Touvron 等人，2019）
Despite this handicap, CLIP features transfer surprisingly well to this task. CLIP matches the best prior result on UCF101 in a linear probe evaluation setting and also outperforms all other models in our evaluation suite. On Kinetics-700, CLIP also outperforms the fine-tuned I3D baseline from the original paper. Since it does not require a training stage, we report CLIP’s zero-shot performance when averaging predictions across all frames. CLIP also performs well in this setting and on Kinetics-700 its performance is within 1 % 1 % 1%1 \% of the fully supervised I3D baseline which is trained on 545000 labeled videos. Encouraged by these results, we also measure CLIP’s performance on the recently introduced RareAct dataset (Miech et al., 2020a) which was designed to measure zero-shot recognition of unusual actions like “hammering a phone” and “drilling an egg”. CLIP improves over the prior state of the art, a S3D model trained on automatically extracted captions from 100 million instructional videos, by 10 points.
尽管存在这一局限，CLIP 特征在此任务中的迁移表现却出奇地好。在线性探针评估设置下，CLIP 在 UCF101 上匹配了先前的最佳结果，并且在我们评估套件中的所有其他模型中也表现更优。在 Kinetics-700 上，CLIP 同样超越了原论文中经过微调的 I3D 基线模型。由于无需训练阶段，我们报告了 CLIP 在所有帧上平均预测的零样本性能。在此设置下，CLIP 表现良好，在 Kinetics-700 上的性能与全监督 I3D 基线（基于 545,000 个标注视频训练）相差仅 1 % 1 % 1%1 \% 。受这些结果鼓舞，我们还测量了 CLIP 在最近推出的 RareAct 数据集（Miech 等人，2020a）上的表现，该数据集旨在衡量对“用锤子砸手机”“在鸡蛋上钻孔”等罕见动作的零样本识别能力。CLIP 将领先优势扩大了 10 个百分点，超越了先前基于 1 亿条自动提取的 instructional 视频字幕训练的 S3D 模型所保持的最先进水平。
While CLIP has encouragingly strong performance on the task of action recognition, we note that there are many differences between the models being compared beyond just their form of supervision such as model architecture, training data distribution, dataset size, and compute used. Further work is needed to more precisely determine what specific design decisions contribute to achieving high performance on this task.
尽管 CLIP 在动作识别任务上表现出令人鼓舞的强大性能，但我们注意到，除了监督形式不同外，被比较模型之间还存在诸多差异，如模型架构、训练数据分布、数据集规模及所用计算资源等。需要进一步工作来更精确地确定哪些具体设计决策对实现该任务的高性能起到了关键作用。

E.4. Geolocalization  E.4. 地理定位

Another behavior we noticed during the development of CLIP was its ability to recognize many places and locations. To quantify this we created the Country211 dataset as described in Appendix A and report results on it throughout the paper. However it is a new benchmark so to compare with prior work on geolocalization we also report results on the IM2GPS test set from Hays & Efros (2008) in Table 17. Since IM2GPS is a regression benchmark, we guess the GPS coordinates of the nearest image in a set of reference images using CLIP’s embedding space. This is not a zeroshot result since it uses nearest-neighbor regression. Despite querying only 1 million images, which is much less than prior work, CLIP performs similarly to several task specific models. It is not, however, competitive with the current state of the art.
在开发 CLIP 过程中，我们观察到的另一项行为是其能够识别大量地点与位置。为量化这一能力，我们如附录 A 所述创建了 Country211 数据集，并在全文中报告相关结果。由于这是一个新基准，为与先前地理定位研究工作对比，我们同时在表 17 中汇报了基于 Hays & Efros (2008)的 IM2GPS 测试集结果。鉴于 IM2GPS 是回归基准任务，我们利用 CLIP 的嵌入空间，通过最近邻回归方法猜测参考图像集中最近邻图像的 GPS 坐标（这并非零样本结果）。尽管仅查询 100 万张图像（远少于先前研究），CLIP 表现与多个专用模型相当，但尚未达到当前最先进技术水平。

E.5. Robustness to Distribution Shift
E.5. 分布偏移鲁棒性

Section 3.3 provides a high level summary and analysis of ImageNet-related robustness results. We briefly provide some additional numerical details in this appendix. Performance results per dataset are provided in Table 16 and compared with the current state of the art results reported in Taori et al. (2020)'s evaluation suite. Zero-shot CLIP improves the state of the art on 5 of the 7 datasets, ImageNet-R, ObjectNet, ImageNet-Sketch, ImageNet-Vid, and YoutubeBB. CLIP’s improvements are largest on ImageNet-Vid and Youtube-BB due to its flexible zero-shot capability and on ImageNet-R, which likely reflects CLIP’s pre-training distribution including significant amounts of creative content. A similar behavior has been documented for the Instagram pre-trained ResNeXt models as discussed in Taori et al. (2020).
第 3.3 节对 ImageNet 相关鲁棒性结果进行了高层概述与分析。本附录中我们简要补充一些额外的数值细节。各数据集的性能结果详见表 16，并与 Taori 等人(2020)评估套件中报告的最新技术水平进行了对比。零样本 CLIP 在 7 个数据集中的 5 个上实现了性能突破，包括 ImageNet-R、ObjectNet、ImageNet-Sketch、ImageNet-Vid 和 YoutubeBB。得益于其灵活的零样本能力，CLIP 在 ImageNet-Vid 和 Youtube-BB 上的提升最为显著；而在 ImageNet-R 上的优势，可能源于其预训练数据集中包含大量创意内容。类似现象在 Taori 等人(2020)讨论的 Instagram 预训练 ResNeXt 模型中也有记载。

Table 20. CLIP-ViT hyperparameters
表 20. CLIP-ViT 超参数配置
  1. *Equal contribution 1 1 ^(1){ }^{1} OpenAI, San Francisco, CA 94110, USA. Correspondence to: < alec, jongwook } @ } @ }@\} @ openai.com > > >>.
    *同等贡献 1 1 ^(1){ }^{1} OpenAI 公司，美国旧金山 94110。通讯作者： } @ } @ }@\} @ openai.com > > >> 。
  2. 1 1 ^(1){ }^{1} The base query list is all words occurring at least 100 times in the English version of Wikipedia. This is augmented with bi-grams
    1 1 ^(1){ }^{1} 基础查询列表包含英语版维基百科中出现频率不低于 100 次的所有词汇，并进一步加入了具有高逐点互信息的双词组合，以及搜索量超过一定阈值的所有维基百科文章标题。最后，所有尚未列入查询列表的 WordNet 同义词集也被添加进来。
  3. with high pointwise mutual information as well as the names of all Wikipedia articles above a certain search volume. Finally all WordNet synsets not already in the query list are added.
    具有高逐点互信息的双词组合以及所有搜索量超过特定阈值的维基百科文章名称均被纳入其中。此外，未包含在初始查询列表中的所有 WordNet 同义词集也一并加入。
  4. 2 2 ^(2){ }^{2} Alec learned much more about flower species and German traffic signs over the course of this project than he originally anticipated.
    2 2 ^(2){ }^{2} 亚历克在此项目过程中对花卉种类和德国交通标志的了解远超他最初的预期。
  5. 3 3 ^(3){ }^{3} We refer readers to Hendrycks et al. (2020a) for additional experiments and discussion on this claim.
    3 3 ^(3){ }^{3} 关于这一主张的更多实验与讨论，我们建议读者参阅 Hendrycks 等人(2020a)的论文。
  6. 4 4 ^(4){ }^{4} We caution that a zero-shot model can still exploit spurious correlations that are shared between the pre-training and evaluation distributions.
    我们提醒，零样本模型仍可能利用预训练与评估分布之间共有的伪相关性。
  7. 5 5 ^(5){ }^{5} There is not a perfect correspondence between the human few-shot tasks and the model’s few-shot performance since the model cannot refer to sample images in the way that the humans can.
    人类的小样本任务与模型的小样本表现之间并非完美对应，因为模型无法像人类那样参考示例图像。
  8. 6 6 ^(6){ }^{6} FairFace is a face image dataset designed to balance age, gender, and race, in order to reduce asymmetries common in previous face datasets. It categorizes gender into 2 groups: female and male and race into 7 groups: White, Black, Indian, East Asian, Southeast Asian, Middle Eastern, and Latino. There are inherent problems with race and gender classifications, as e.g. Bowker & Star (2000)
    FairFace 是一个旨在平衡年龄、性别和种族的面部图像数据集，以减少以往面部数据集中常见的不对称性。它将性别分为 2 类：女性和男性；种族分为 7 类：白人、黑人、印度人、东亚人、东南亚人、中东人和拉丁裔。种族和性别分类存在固有问题，如 Bowker & Star（2000 年）所述。
  9. 8 8 ^(8){ }^{8} Note: The CelebA dataset is more representative of faces with lighter skin tones. Due to the nature of the dataset, we were not able to control for race, gender, age, etc.
    注：CelebA 数据集对浅肤色面孔更具代表性。由于数据集特性，我们无法控制种族、性别、年龄等因素。
  10. 9 9 ^(9){ }^{9} A model could be unfit for use due to inadequate performance or due to the inappropriateness of AI use in the application area itself.
    9 9 ^(9){ }^{9} 模型可能因性能不足或 AI 在应用领域本身的不适用性而不适合使用。
